524
00:35:35,160 --> 00:35:36,940
I was left with no choice.

525
00:35:36,940 --> 00:35:39,880
Teacher wanted to get acquainted with that Fuyao through her.

526
00:35:39,880 --> 00:35:43,000
But the wrong person came today and said the wrong things.

527
00:35:43,000 --> 00:35:46,300
So, they must die.

528
00:35:46,300 --> 00:35:51,830
What kind of teacher takes someone's life to get acquainted with another one?

529
00:35:51,830 --> 00:35:54,140
So evil!

530
00:35:55,140 --> 00:35:59,070
I'll say it one more time: let them go.

531
00:35:59,070 --> 00:36:01,730
- Based on what?
- Based on the fact that your teacher is my teacher's junior.

532
00:36:01,730 --> 00:36:04,610
I'll beg for forgiveness later.

533
00:36:04,610 --> 00:36:06,610
Zhan Beiye, leave with Yalan Zhu first.

534
00:36:06,610 --> 00:36:09,380
- Then you?
- Don't worry. I'll be fine.

535
00:36:12,960 --> 00:36:14,920
