543
00:37:03,770 --> 00:37:05,790
It's none of your business.

544
00:37:07,210 --> 00:37:10,790
Don't forget the person that Firmament is asking you to find!

545
00:37:29,570 --> 00:37:32,270
You are the one predestined by the Mystic Spirit Leaf.

546
00:37:32,270 --> 00:37:36,460
Only you can change the universe. Find the girl with the Five-Colored Stone

547
00:37:36,460 --> 00:37:41,240
or else the Five Regions will once again be doomed eternally because of her.

548
00:38:21,930 --> 00:38:24,460
What are you thinking about?

549
00:38:24,460 --> 00:38:26,850
Thinking about you.

550
00:38:26,850 --> 00:38:29,710
To celebrate Zhuzhu coming back, I'll invite you to a drink.

551
00:38:29,710 --> 00:38:31,170
Okay.

